Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.02,0:00:07.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是初期开发型试作0号机
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.90,0:00:09.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,SKYKNIGHT和FIREBRAND哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.32,0:00:11.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出现了众多受害者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.31,0:00:15.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,LUXON和BRADYON的前代机体
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.48,0:00:17.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.56,0:00:22.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不清楚呢 不过现在也在定期进行保养
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.44,0:00:25.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 为什么这种东西会在夏威夷基地？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.38,0:00:28.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然也有研究的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.59,0:00:31.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过更多还是为了保管资料吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.06,0:00:34.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快 正在开发的新型机也要完工了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.33,0:00:37.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这机体不会再起飞了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.53,0:00:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是费尔米老师开发的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.08,0:00:42.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然很难过…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.30,0:00:47.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mayday Mayday
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.30,0:00:47.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Mayday：国际通用的无线电通话遇难求救讯号
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.71,0:00:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是Transport Airlines 507航班
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.15,0:00:51.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左引擎起火
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.51,0:00:53.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请求紧急降落夏威夷基地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.91,0:00:57.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白 使用2号跑道 消防队赶快出动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.55,0:01:08.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.99,0:01:10.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是民营机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.80,0:01:11.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.19,0:01:14.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警报也没响 应该不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.15,0:01:19.85,zm,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}夏威夷基地·第5大门
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.35,0:01:28.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.68,0:01:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.12,0:01:35.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爆炸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.04,0:01:42.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然是valiancer
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.73,0:01:47.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紧急通知 紧急通知
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.06,0:01:49.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人valiancer出现在基地内
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.19,0:01:53.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌方间谍似乎已经潜入 各部队…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.42,0:01:57.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们急的就像热锅上的蚂蚁啊 真可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.33,0:02:00.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也表现的着急一点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.15,0:02:02.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可就要让您大失所望了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.91,0:02:09.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 我们去捕食猎物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.20,0:02:16.08,OPJ,NTP,0,0,0,,羽撃(はばた)け
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.20,0:02:16.08,OPZ,NTP,0,0,0,,展翅高飞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.10,0:02:20.48,OPJ,NTP,0,0,0,,まだ見ぬ空に　希望(ひかり)重ねて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.10,0:02:20.48,OPZ,NTP,0,0,0,,向那未知的天空 将希望重叠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.86,0:02:24.00,OPJ,NTP,0,0,0,,哀しみの重さに　負けたりしないで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.86,0:02:24.00,OPZ,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不要被那沉重的悲伤压倒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.08,0:02:29.04,OPJ,NTP,0,0,0,,永遠に響け　UNISONIA
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.08,0:02:29.04,OPZ,NTP,0,0,0,,响彻永远吧 UNISONIA
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.37,0:02:37.67,OPJ,NTP,0,0,0,,君が見てるその世界は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.37,0:02:37.67,OPZ,NTP,0,0,0,,你眼中的那个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.89,0:02:44.12,OPJ,NTP,0,0,0,,どんな色をしてるのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.89,0:02:44.12,OPZ,NTP,0,0,0,,呈现出了何种颜色呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.19,0:02:46.12,OPJ,NTP,0,0,0,,(Measure feeling match)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.19,0:02:46.12,OPZ,NTP,0,0,0,,(Measure feeling match)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.48,0:02:48.85,OPJ,NTP,0,0,0,,失くす痛みなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.48,0:02:48.85,OPZ,NTP,0,0,0,,明明不想去习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:51.74,OPJ,NTP,0,0,0,,慣れたくはないのに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:51.74,OPZ,NTP,0,0,0,,失去的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.80,0:02:56.19,OPJ,NTP,0,0,0,,こんな夜も星はきれいだね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.80,0:02:56.19,OPZ,NTP,0,0,0,,就算这种夜晚星空也是如此地美丽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.88,0:03:00.80,OPJ,NTP,0,0,0,,手のひらからこぼれ落ちてく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.88,0:03:00.80,OPZ,NTP,0,0,0,,就像那从手心中慢慢滑落的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.80,0:03:03.76,OPJ,NTP,0,0,0,,錆びれたコインのように
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.80,0:03:03.76,OPZ,NTP,0,0,0,,锈迹斑斑的硬币
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.97,0:03:06.88,OPJ,NTP,0,0,0,,(モドレナイ)(カエリタイ)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.97,0:03:06.88,OPZ,NTP,0,0,0,,（无法回头 想重新来过）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.88,0:03:10.11,OPJ,NTP,0,0,0,,背中合わせのふたり
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.88,0:03:10.11,OPZ,NTP,0,0,0,,背靠背的两人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.46,0:03:12.24,OPJ,NTP,0,0,0,,穿撃(つらぬ)け
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.46,0:03:12.24,OPZ,NTP,0,0,0,,刺穿一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.29,0:03:16.80,OPJ,NTP,0,0,0,,褪せない想い　絆に変えて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.29,0:03:16.80,OPZ,NTP,0,0,0,,永不褪色的思念 转变成为永久的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.05,0:03:20.22,OPJ,NTP,0,0,0,,色のない世界を塗り替えるように
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.05,0:03:20.22,OPZ,NTP,0,0,0,,为了将那无色的世界重新涂过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.29,0:03:22.94,OPJ,NTP,0,0,0,,届け　このシンパシー
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.29,0:03:22.94,OPZ,NTP,0,0,0,,请传达到吧 这个共鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.96,0:03:24.29,OPJ,NTP,0,0,0,,Growing the wing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.96,0:03:24.29,OPZ,NTP,0,0,0,,Growing the wing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.47,0:03:29.24,OPJ,NTP,0,0,0,,想い通りの　未来を創ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.47,0:03:29.24,OPZ,NTP,0,0,0,,一起来创造 梦想中的未来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:32.31,OPJ,NTP,0,0,0,,運命さえ　変えてゆける
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:32.31,OPZ,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是命运 我们也能改变
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:37.44,OPJ,NTP,0,0,0,,時を越えて　UNISONIA
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:37.44,OPZ,NTP,0,0,0,,穿越时空思念 UNISONIA
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.69,0:03:44.92,biaoti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\pos(1106,589)}真实
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.93,0:03:44.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.95,0:03:50.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是父亲的脸 我在课堂上画的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.53,0:03:57.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师也夸我画得好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.29,0:03:59.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.10,0:04:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:02.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.86,0:04:06.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去念士官学校？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.75,0:04:07.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:09.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.17,0:04:11.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要成为保护祖国佐基利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.86,0:04:14.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护居住在这个国家的人民的军人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.39,0:04:17.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像父亲一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.79,0:04:27.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.15,0:04:30.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:35.25,zm,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}夏威夷基地·第7装备楼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.37,0:04:38.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.20,0:04:44.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.40,0:04:46.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请告诉我们详细的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.27,0:04:49.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像你们在广播中听到的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.43,0:04:51.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在敌军士兵侵入到了基地内部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:53.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在各处进行破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.81,0:04:55.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认到的valiancer有8台
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.07,0:04:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塔基姆 差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:04:59.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我还没玩够 不过没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.79,0:05:03.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中两台脱离上空
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.18,0:05:07.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停靠整备场似乎正发生枪击战 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.58,0:05:08.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.83,0:05:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不明白敌人的目的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.83,0:05:16.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为侵入如此规模的基地 就只有8台valiancer哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.27,0:05:18.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算问司令部该如何应对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.32,0:05:21.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也只是一边倒的告诉我们「打倒敌人 保护基地」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.70,0:05:23.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我们该做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.72,0:05:28.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 因此 我们采取独自行动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.92,0:05:31.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾维拉君和小真由立刻回到舰内
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.52,0:05:32.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青叶君和迪奥去回收搬入基地第7装备楼的LUXON和BRADYON
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.34,0:05:40.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗洛姆君担任他们俩的护卫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.67,0:05:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.95,0:05:43.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.99,0:05:48.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道敌人会藏在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.69,0:05:52.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想死的话 就自己保护好自己
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.22,0:05:53.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.95,0:06:38.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舱门就这么开着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.68,0:06:39.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.07,0:06:43.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.08,0:06:44.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.05,0:06:45.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.81,0:06:46.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.03,0:06:49.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过要花费点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:51.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越快越好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.36,0:06:51.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:53.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对面的情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.06,0:06:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在交战 大概能坚持住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.87,0:07:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 解除启动的安全保护一完成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.10,0:07:02.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就开始撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.77,0:07:03.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.00,0:07:11.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,取得联系啊 告诉佐基利亚 雏在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.93,0:07:16.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那样的话 雏就会成为我们的俘虏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.44,0:07:19.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想那样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.76,0:07:27.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.91,0:07:34.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.75,0:07:35.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.46,0:07:36.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:42.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暴露了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.79,0:07:45.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在自己的基地还真是乱来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.79,0:07:48.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点 到这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.89,0:07:49.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.23,0:07:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.18,0:07:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏 少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:02.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐为少佐包扎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.15,0:08:06.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们和别动队会合 确保退路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.94,0:08:07.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.71,0:08:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我们走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.77,0:08:13.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得快点止血
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.88,0:08:15.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.11,0:08:17.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.50,0:08:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有件事要告诉你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:22.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.86,0:08:23.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会影响到伤口的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.91,0:08:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.48,0:08:26.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:37.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏 你并不是我的亲生女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青叶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.86,0:08:50.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:51.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被分开了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.34,0:08:54.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们从这边的路去目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.53,0:08:57.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你找到迂回路过去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.50,0:08:58.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.90,0:08:59.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:09.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是十年前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.38,0:09:16.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被配属到激战地萨格勒布的我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.36,0:09:22.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在被烧光的战场 遇到了你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.36,0:09:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时的你穿着破破烂烂的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.09,0:09:30.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几乎不能说话 失去了记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.45,0:09:36.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能记住的只有雏这个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.46,0:09:43.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把你当做战争孤儿领了回去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.89,0:09:47.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样 我和你成为了父女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.26,0:09:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:55.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你突然告诉我这样的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.74,0:09:58.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难以相信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.47,0:10:04.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,濒死之人 是不会开玩笑说这种事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.91,0:10:10.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓紧 不能再继续让佐基利亚为所欲为了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.93,0:10:14.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧 雏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.58,0:10:18.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在敌人来之前 逃离这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.64,0:10:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话父亲也跟我一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.25,0:10:23.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经没救了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.67,0:10:24.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.79,0:10:25.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.36,0:10:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.55,0:10:29.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.20,0:10:34.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后就让我作为一个父亲耍下帅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.41,0:10:36.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.46,0:10:38.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:41.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧 雏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.00,0:10:45.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.60,0:10:48.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.58,0:11:09.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.68,0:11:10.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.75,0:11:13.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了以防万一 还是给他一枪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.12,0:11:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不解风情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.36,0:11:19.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正沉浸在和女儿的回忆中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.15,0:11:21.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.09,0:11:24.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我带你们一起去地狱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.75,0:11:30.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又爆炸了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.59,0:11:34.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 我只是个高中生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算突然让我开枪也开不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.31,0:11:39.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 这里是哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.44,0:11:47.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.40,0:11:54.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你并不是我的亲生女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.76,0:11:58.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能记住的只有雏这个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.01,0:12:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.56,0:12:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你带我来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.89,0:12:12.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说 你是我的同班同学 叫弓原雏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.52,0:12:15.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 她在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.28,0:12:25.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.62,0:12:31.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏？你怎么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.26,0:12:34.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说入侵的敌军士兵是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.30,0:12:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…并不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.52,0:12:44.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是什么人 是青叶所说的雏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.29,0:12:47.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.60,0:12:48.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.31,0:12:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少佐他？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.41,0:12:57.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 在我离开的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:12:58.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.81,0:12:59.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.35,0:13:02.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎没被卷入爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.33,0:13:05.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 掩护我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.78,0:13:06.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.71,0:13:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 你打算去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.79,0:13:09.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.67,0:13:11.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后面自动进行就会结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.17,0:13:13.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去找雏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.55,0:13:28.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 里亚赞少佐他…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.29,0:13:29.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.96,0:13:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作战可以继续吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.85,0:13:36.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然会有推迟 还在估计范围内
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:40.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那么接下来现场的指挥就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.66,0:13:43.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这边也会按照预定开始行动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.90,0:13:44.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.13,0:13:45.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.42,0:13:47.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.99,0:13:51.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在把作战成功当做最优先考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.39,0:13:59.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.34,0:14:01.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:06.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定我是青叶所说的雏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.94,0:14:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话 失忆的事也多少能理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.23,0:14:13.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我不明白为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.49,0:14:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.52,0:14:19.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的 我到底是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.02,0:14:21.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.08,0:14:26.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来这边吧 雏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.36,0:14:30.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到我们这里 到Cygnus来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.87,0:14:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.30,0:14:33.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.67,0:14:36.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也接纳了从70年前来的我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.73,0:14:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是敌人 只要说清楚大家一定会明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.29,0:14:42.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且也有值得信赖的人在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.65,0:14:45.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他叫迪奥 虽然有点臭屁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.20,0:14:48.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.72,0:14:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保证
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.77,0:14:52.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.44,0:14:57.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我连自己是谁都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.58,0:15:00.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏就是雏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.95,0:15:03.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是一直生活在这里的雏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.29,0:15:05.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是和我是同班同学的雏都没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.83,0:15:06.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏就是雏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.23,0:15:08.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会毫无保留地接受你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.90,0:15:09.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.93,0:15:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.79,0:15:17.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.01,0:15:18.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.11,0:15:19.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.59,0:15:21.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那家伙身边离开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.10,0:15:22.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比森
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.75,0:15:23.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.57,0:15:25.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.49,0:15:30.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新型机的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.84,0:15:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏 你果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.53,0:15:33.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.98,0:15:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么为什么要袒护他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.48,0:15:36.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个男人是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:37.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.67,0:15:39.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下啊 听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.05,0:15:39.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.98,0:15:42.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏 你不是佐基利亚的军人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.52,0:15:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我们的同伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.70,0:15:47.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以来一起战斗至今的我们 为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.45,0:15:49.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.40,0:15:53.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里亚赞少佐 并不是为了让你做那样的事才死的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:56.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你连父亲也要背叛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.69,0:15:58.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.13,0:16:03.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.51,0:16:04.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.75,0:16:06.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.77,0:16:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比森
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.82,0:16:17.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青叶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.30,0:16:19.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.78,0:16:20.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别追了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.56,0:16:21.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:25.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗洛姆 把那个笨蛋拉到一旁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.41,0:16:26.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.57,0:16:28.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 快点藏起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.84,0:16:29.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下再说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.14,0:16:31.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快安全保护的解除就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.28,0:16:35.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的任务是夺取联合的新型valiancer
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.96,0:16:36.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.76,0:16:41.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.51,0:16:42.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:46.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青叶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:49.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青叶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.46,0:16:58.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地上似乎安静下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.52,0:17:00.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们把上空的两台打下来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.75,0:17:04.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊 要在他们落下来之前好好揍一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:06.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.71,0:17:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷达感应 出现多数热源
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.80,0:17:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是导弹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.65,0:17:11.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,nectar屏障展开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.54,0:17:13.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最大限度扩展
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.85,0:17:15.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要让他们落入基地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.81,0:17:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 这是干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.56,0:17:27.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不攻占基地 而是打算破坏？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.44,0:17:52.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪奥 青叶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.29,0:17:55.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于出来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.39,0:17:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:17:57.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是敌人坐在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.14,0:17:58.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被抢走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.40,0:18:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.67,0:18:05.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,击落它
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.72,0:18:07.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.72,0:18:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比被敌人夺走要好得多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.25,0:18:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.43,0:18:12.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏坐在那上面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.15,0:18:14.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,击落什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.41,0:18:15.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我差不多一点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:18.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不知道现在发生了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.05,0:18:20.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是雏所希望的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.05,0:18:21.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.71,0:18:23.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏现在很烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.52,0:18:24.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她父亲去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:27.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得自己不知道自己是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.69,0:18:29.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是能做出这种事的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.87,0:18:31.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 现在联结机…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.80,0:18:34.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想打落那样的雏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.46,0:18:35.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会让你们打落的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.10,0:18:46.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青叶同学和迪奥…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.39,0:18:47.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.27,0:18:52.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们无法用联结系统
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.48,0:18:53.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一口气决胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.96,0:18:54.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.73,0:18:55.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.85,0:18:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那机体非常危险
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.57,0:18:58.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上回基地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.43,0:19:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 艾维拉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.77,0:19:05.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把两台机体的远程访问优先权转给我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.53,0:19:07.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须要让他们无法联结
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.98,0:19:08.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.37,0:19:11.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明白我们的目的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.77,0:19:13.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是夺回LUXON和BRADYON而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.17,0:19:15.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.77,0:19:17.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们上 连接迪奥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.11,0:19:18.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.42,0:19:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,SKYKNIGHT和FIREBRAND联结成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.57,0:19:47.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能 这种设定为什么还能成功
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.51,0:20:08.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 座舱不同 行动也不方便了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.45,0:20:10.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比森 来了哦 是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.65,0:20:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 这些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.34,0:20:21.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏 你坐在那个上面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.31,0:20:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个声音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.34,0:20:24.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 现在还来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.32,0:20:26.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青叶…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.60,0:20:30.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从雏身边滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.84,0:20:34.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青叶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.73,0:20:37.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙 只有你这家伙我要在这里杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.80,0:20:39.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 不要妨碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.93,0:20:42.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开青叶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.21,0:20:44.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.18,0:20:48.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们俩的emphatier波形！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.82,0:20:49.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.93,0:21:15.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比森
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.71,0:21:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那是什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.68,0:21:26.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作战目的达成了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.91,0:21:28.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始回收
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.66,0:21:30.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全体机体在抵达合流地点前分散开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.15,0:21:32.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.70,0:21:35.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更多的战斗行为是没有意义的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.09,0:21:38.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 比森
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.97,0:21:50.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.78,0:21:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别逃啊 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.37,0:22:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚…刚才那个是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.19,0:22:15.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青叶 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.88,0:23:41.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 BUDDY COMPLEX 二人之绊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.97,0:23:41.82,biaoti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(630,486)}下回「二人之绊」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.26,0:22:25.23,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,心で呼ぶ　惹かれあう彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.26,0:22:25.23,EDZ,NTP,0,0,0,,心的呼应 响应的彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.33,0:22:33.88,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,痛みの理由(わけ)も忘れて　今だけどうか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.33,0:22:33.88,EDZ,NTP,0,0,0,,痛的理由 请暂且忘记 我在此深深祈求
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.24,0:22:43.08,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,キミを知っている　キミを探しているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.24,0:22:43.08,EDZ,NTP,0,0,0,,我深知你 我在一直寻找着你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.12,0:22:51.80,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,引き止められない光の残像に　そっとくちづけて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.12,0:22:51.80,EDZ,NTP,0,0,0,,轻轻吻向那已飘渺的光的残像
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.96,0:23:00.81,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,躊躇いが僅かな　希望への糸口なら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.96,0:23:00.81,EDZ,NTP,0,0,0,,你那稍稍的犹豫不决 成为了那连接希望的蛛丝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.84,0:23:09.52,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,彷徨った数だけ　優しい朝へ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.84,0:23:09.52,EDZ,NTP,0,0,0,,你那微微的彷徨 拉近了与那温柔黎明的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.82,0:23:18.56,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,あの空に還る未来で　救いたい　守りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.82,0:23:18.56,EDZ,NTP,0,0,0,,想去拯救 想去保护 那早已归还于天空的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.57,0:23:25.44,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,その夢に届く未来で　待っていて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.57,0:23:25.44,EDZ,NTP,0,0,0,,请留步 那已经早已传达过梦想的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.63,0:23:34.86,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,きっと出会える愛に　手を伸ばして欲しい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.63,0:23:34.86,EDZ,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能与我一起去抓住 那注定相遇的爱
